<HEAD>Congressmen Warn Against Complacency In Anti-Abortion Movement</HEAD>
<HEAD>Eds: LEADS with 9 grafs to UPDATE with Missouri governor blaming
abortion for problems of youth; picks up 6th graf, `In the...'</HEAD>
<HEAD>With AM-Abortion Opponents, Bjt</HEAD>
<DATELINE>BLOOMINGTON, Minn. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
