l that spilled, a relatively light form of oil compared with the crude oil that has caused such problems on <LOCATION> Alaska </LOCATION> beaches, has largely evaporated or dissipated. The Coast Guard vessels were not scheduled to accompany the tanker all the way to <LOCATION> New </LOCATION> <LOCATION> York </LOCATION>.
